{
  "video_id": "dWObti8KNc4",
  "title": "The power of herd immunity (with English subtitles) | Romina Libster",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Gisela Giardino Reviewer: Romina Pol"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12280.0,
      "end_time": 17600.0,
      "text": "One of the first patients I had to see as a pediatrician was Sol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17370.0,
      "end_time": 20150.0,
      "text": "a beautiful month-old baby"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20150.0,
      "end_time": 23830.0,
      "text": "who was admitted with signs of a severe respiratory infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23830.0,
      "end_time": 28110.0,
      "text": "Until then, I had never seen a patient worsen so fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28810.0,
      "end_time": 31810.0,
      "text": "In just two days she was connected to a respirator"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31810.0,
      "end_time": 34550.0,
      "text": "and on the third day she died."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34550.0,
      "end_time": 37300.0,
      "text": "Sol had whooping cough."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37300.0,
      "end_time": 42100.0,
      "text": "After discussing the case in the room and after a quite distressing catharsis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42460.0,
      "end_time": 44509.0,
      "text": "I remember my chief resident said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44509.0,
      "end_time": 47850.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, take a deep breath. Wash your face."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48430.0,
      "end_time": 51500.0,
      "text": "And now comes the hardest part:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51500.0,
      "end_time": 53459.0,
      "text": "We have to go talk to her parents.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54150.0,
      "end_time": 58120.0,
      "text": "At that time, a thousand questions came to mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58120.0,
      "end_time": 62449.0,
      "text": "from, \"How could a one-month-old baby be so unfortunate?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63200.0,
      "end_time": 66700.0,
      "text": "to, \"Could we have done something about it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67400.0,
      "end_time": 69680.0,
      "text": "Before vaccines existed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69680.0,
      "end_time": 74550.0,
      "text": "many infectious diseases killed millions of people per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75100.0,
      "end_time": 78630.0,
      "text": "During the 1918 flu pandemic"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78630.0,
      "end_time": 81780.0,
      "text": "50 million people died."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81780.0,
      "end_time": 85600.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s greater than Argentina&#39;s current population."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85600.0,
      "end_time": 89110.0,
      "text": "Perhaps, the older ones among you remember the polio epidemic"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89110.0,
      "end_time": 92300.0,
      "text": "that occurred in Argentina in 1956."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92240.0,
      "end_time": 95559.0,
      "text": "At that time, there was no vaccine available against polio."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95560.0,
      "end_time": 98900.0,
      "text": "People didn&#39;t know what to do. They were going crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98900.0,
      "end_time": 100370.0,
      "text": "They would go painting trees with caustic lime."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100370.0,
      "end_time": 101940.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d put little bags of camphor"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101940.0,
      "end_time": 105460.0,
      "text": "in their children&#39;s underwear, as if that could do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106800.0,
      "end_time": 110600.0,
      "text": "During the polio epidemic, thousands of people died."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110600.0,
      "end_time": 114770.0,
      "text": "And thousands of people were left with very significant neurological damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116650.0,
      "end_time": 119290.0,
      "text": "I know this because I read about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119290.0,
      "end_time": 123800.0,
      "text": "because thanks to vaccines, my generation was lucky"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 125890.0,
      "text": "to not live through an epidemic as terrible as this."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125890.0,
      "end_time": 130680.0,
      "text": "Vaccines are one of the great successes of the 20th century&#39;s public health."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131210.0,
      "end_time": 133230.0,
      "text": "After potable water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 133230.0,
      "end_time": 136840.0,
      "text": "they are the interventions that have most reduced mortality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 136840.0,
      "end_time": 138970.0,
      "text": "even more than antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 139570.0,
      "end_time": 144560.0,
      "text": "Vaccines eradicated terrible diseases such as smallpox from the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144590.0,
      "end_time": 148200.0,
      "text": "and succeeded in significantly reducing mortality"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148200.0,
      "end_time": 150450.0,
      "text": "due to other diseases such as measles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150450.0,
      "end_time": 153780.0,
      "text": "whooping cough, polio and many more."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154320.0,
      "end_time": 161200.0,
      "text": "All these diseases are considered vaccine-preventable diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 161910.0,
      "end_time": 163670.0,
      "text": "What does this mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 163670.0,
      "end_time": 166690.0,
      "text": "That they are potentially preventable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166690.0,
      "end_time": 169660.0,
      "text": "but in order to be so, something must be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169660.0,
      "end_time": 171760.0,
      "text": "You need to get vaccinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 172270.0,
      "end_time": 175970.0,
      "text": "I imagine that most, if not all of us here today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175970.0,
      "end_time": 179210.0,
      "text": "received a vaccine at some point in our life."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180510.0,
      "end_time": 184959.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not so sure that many of us know"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 184960.0,
      "end_time": 189290.0,
      "text": "which vaccines or boosters we should receive after adolescence."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 190710.0,
      "end_time": 194790.0,
      "text": "Have you ever wondered who we are protecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 194790.0,
      "end_time": 196640.0,
      "text": "when we vaccinate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 197700.0,
      "end_time": 198700.0,
      "text": "What do I mean by that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 198700.0,
      "end_time": 203670.0,
      "text": "Is there any other effect beyond protecting ourselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 205500.0,
      "end_time": 207170.0,
      "text": "Let me show you something."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 207760.0,
      "end_time": 210220.0,
      "text": "Imagine for a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 210220.0,
      "end_time": 212230.0,
      "text": "that we are in a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 212230.0,
      "end_time": 215480.0,
      "text": "that has never had a case of a particular disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 215480.0,
      "end_time": 217179.0,
      "text": "such as the measles."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 217430.0,
      "end_time": 222290.0,
      "text": "This would mean that no one in the city has ever had contact with the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222290.0,
      "end_time": 226880.0,
      "text": "No one has natural defenses against, nor been vaccinated against measles."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 227680.0,
      "end_time": 232420.0,
      "text": "If one day, a person sick with the measles appears in this city"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 233000.0,
      "end_time": 236510.0,
      "text": "the disease won&#39;t find much resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 236510.0,
      "end_time": 239440.0,
      "text": "and will begin spreading from person to person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 239440.0,
      "end_time": 243500.0,
      "text": "and in no time it will disseminate throughout the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 243810.0,
      "end_time": 245530.0,
      "text": "After a certain time"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 245530.0,
      "end_time": 248900.0,
      "text": "a big part of the population will be ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 249750.0,
      "end_time": 253910.0,
      "text": "This happened when there were no vaccines."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 254630.0,
      "end_time": 259110.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine the complete opposite case."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 259420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261830.00000000003,
      "text": "We are in a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 261829.0,
      "end_time": 264650.0,
      "text": "where more than 90 percent of the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 264650.0,
      "end_time": 267990.0,
      "text": "has defenses against the measles, which means"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 267100.0,
      "end_time": 270839.0,
      "text": "that they either had the disease, survived, and developed natural defenses;"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 270839.0,
      "end_time": 274540.0,
      "text": "or that they had been immunized against measles."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275200.0,
      "end_time": 276810.0,
      "text": "If one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 276810.0,
      "end_time": 280740.0,
      "text": "a person sick with the measles appears in this city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 281230.0,
      "end_time": 284610.0,
      "text": "the disease will find much more resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284610.0,
      "end_time": 288100.0,
      "text": "and won&#39;t be transmitted that much from person to person."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 288780.0,
      "end_time": 292330.0,
      "text": "The spread will probably remain contained"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 292750.0,
      "end_time": 295680.0,
      "text": "and a measles outbreak won&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 297600.0,
      "end_time": 299760.0,
      "text": "I would like you to pay attention to something."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 300810.0,
      "end_time": 303490.0,
      "text": "People who are vaccinated"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 303490.0,
      "end_time": 306290.0,
      "text": "are not only protecting themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 306290.0,
      "end_time": 309900.0,
      "text": "but by blocking the dissemination of the disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 309900.0,
      "end_time": 311539.0,
      "text": "within the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 311540.0,
      "end_time": 316220.0,
      "text": "they are indirectly protecting the people in this community"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 316220.0,
      "end_time": 318390.0,
      "text": "who are not vaccinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 318690.0,
      "end_time": 321660.0,
      "text": "They create a kind of protective shield"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 321660.0,
      "end_time": 324760.0,
      "text": "which prevents them from coming in contact with the disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 324760.0,
      "end_time": 327380.0,
      "text": "so that these people are protected."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 328670.0,
      "end_time": 331870.0,
      "text": "This indirect protection"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 331870.0,
      "end_time": 335370.0,
      "text": "that the unvaccinated people within a community receive"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 335370.0,
      "end_time": 339380.0,
      "text": "simply by being surrounded by vaccinated people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 339950.0,
      "end_time": 343100.0,
      "text": "is called herd immunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 345130.0,
      "end_time": 347590.0,
      "text": "Many people in the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 347590.0,
      "end_time": 351900.0,
      "text": "depend almost exclusively on this herd immunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 351900.0,
      "end_time": 353750.0,
      "text": "to be protected against disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 354760.0,
      "end_time": 358719.0,
      "text": "The unvaccinated people you see in infographics are not just hypothetical."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362599.0,
      "text": "Those people are our nieces and nephews, our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 362600.0,
      "end_time": 365970.0,
      "text": "who may be too young to receive their first shots."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 367100.0,
      "end_time": 369410.0,
      "text": "They are our parents, our siblings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 369410.0,
      "end_time": 370840.0,
      "text": "our acquaintances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 370840.0,
      "end_time": 372710.0,
      "text": "who may have a disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372710.0,
      "end_time": 376359.0,
      "text": "or take medication that lowers their defenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 378100.0,
      "end_time": 382800.0,
      "text": "There are also people who are allergic to a particular vaccine."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 383350.0,
      "end_time": 385750.0,
      "text": "They could even be among us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 385750.0,
      "end_time": 387610.0,
      "text": "any of us who got vaccinated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 387610.0,
      "end_time": 391410.0,
      "text": "but the vaccine didn&#39;t produce the expected effect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 391410.0,
      "end_time": 395600.0,
      "text": "because not all vaccines are always 100 percent effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 395600.0,
      "end_time": 400800.0,
      "text": "All these people depend almost exclusively on herd immunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 400800.0,
      "end_time": 403360.0,
      "text": "to be protected against diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 404390.0,
      "end_time": 409200.0,
      "text": "To achieve this effect of herd immunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 409200.0,
      "end_time": 413870.0,
      "text": "it is necessary that a large percentage of the population be vaccinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 414500.0,
      "end_time": 417570.0,
      "text": "This percentage is called the threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 417570.0,
      "end_time": 421330.0,
      "text": "The threshold depends on many variables:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 421330.0,
      "end_time": 423740.0,
      "text": "It depends on the germ&#39;s characteristics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 423740.0,
      "end_time": 428400.0,
      "text": "and those of the immune response that the vaccine generates."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 428400.0,
      "end_time": 430430.0,
      "text": "But they all have something in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 430430.0,
      "end_time": 435640.0,
      "text": "If the percentage of the population in a vaccinated community"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 435980.0,
      "end_time": 439500.0,
      "text": "is below this threshold number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 439500.0,
      "end_time": 443110.0,
      "text": "the disease will begin to spread more freely"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 443110.0,
      "end_time": 447780.0,
      "text": "and may generate an outbreak of this disease within the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 447780.0,
      "end_time": 454859.0,
      "text": "Even diseases which were  at some point controlled may reappear."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 456550.0,
      "end_time": 458740.0,
      "text": "This is not just a theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 458740.0,
      "end_time": 461100.0,
      "text": "This has happened, and is still happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 463500.0,
      "end_time": 467750.0,
      "text": "In 1998, a British researcher published an article"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 467750.0,
      "end_time": 470530.0,
      "text": "in one of the most important medical journals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 470530.0,
      "end_time": 473150.0,
      "text": "saying that the MMR vaccine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 473150.0,
      "end_time": 475880.0,
      "text": "which is given for measles, mumps and rubella,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 475880.0,
      "end_time": 477750.0,
      "text": "was associated with autism."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 477750.0,
      "end_time": 480450.0,
      "text": "This generated an immediate impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 481100.0,
      "end_time": 485659.0,
      "text": "People began to stop getting vaccinated, and stopped vaccinating their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 485680.0,
      "end_time": 487300.0,
      "text": "And what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 487300.0,
      "end_time": 489980.0,
      "text": "The number of people vaccinated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 489980.0,
      "end_time": 493960.0,
      "text": "in many communities around the world, fell below this threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 493960.0,
      "end_time": 497520.0,
      "text": "And there were outbreaks of measles in many cities in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 497520.0,
      "end_time": 499960.0,
      "text": "in the U.S., in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 499960.0,
      "end_time": 502120.0,
      "text": "Many people got sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 502120.0,
      "end_time": 504900.0,
      "text": "People died of measles."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 505870.0,
      "end_time": 507350.0,
      "text": "What happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 507350.0,
      "end_time": 511470.0,
      "text": "This article also generated a huge stir within the medical community."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 512200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515689.00000000006,
      "text": "Dozens of researchers began to assess if this was actually true."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 517130.0,
      "end_time": 520419.0,
      "text": "Not only could no one find"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 520419.0,
      "end_time": 525669.0,
      "text": "a causal association between MMR and autism at the population level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 525669.0,
      "end_time": 530569.0,
      "text": "but it was also found that this article had incorrect claims."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 530820.0,
      "end_time": 533370.0,
      "text": "Even more, it was fraudulent."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 534120.0,
      "end_time": 536510.0,
      "text": "It was fraudulent."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 537120.0,
      "end_time": 543550.0,
      "text": "In fact, the journal publicly retracted the article in 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 544880.0,
      "end_time": 548780.0,
      "text": "One of the main concerns and excuses for not getting vaccinated"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 548780.0,
      "end_time": 550970.0,
      "text": "are the adverse effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 551770.0,
      "end_time": 557410.0,
      "text": "Vaccines, like other drugs, can have potential adverse effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 557970.0,
      "end_time": 560480.0,
      "text": "Most are mild and temporary."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 560480.0,
      "end_time": 566470.0,
      "text": "But the benefits are always greater than possible complications."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 567740.0,
      "end_time": 572300.0,
      "text": "When we are ill, we want to heal fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 572300.0,
      "end_time": 574420.0,
      "text": "Many of us who are here"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 574420.0,
      "end_time": 578890.0,
      "text": "take antibiotics when we have an infection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 578900.0,
      "end_time": 581270.0,
      "text": "we take anti-hypertensives when we have high blood pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 581270.0,
      "end_time": 583449.0,
      "text": "we take cardiac medications."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 583450.0,
      "end_time": 586700.0,
      "text": "Why? Because we are sick and we want to heal fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 586700.0,
      "end_time": 588720.0,
      "text": "And we don&#39;t question it much."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 588720.0,
      "end_time": 593150.0,
      "text": "Why is it so difficult to think of preventing diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 593890.0,
      "end_time": 597100.0,
      "text": "by taking care of ourselves when we are healthy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 597100.0,
      "end_time": 600290.0,
      "text": "We take care of ourselves a lot when affected by an illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 600290.0,
      "end_time": 603250.0,
      "text": "or in situations of imminent danger."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 604140.0,
      "end_time": 606810.0,
      "text": "I imagine most of us here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 606810.0,
      "end_time": 610540.0,
      "text": "remember the influenza-A pandemic"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 610540.0,
      "end_time": 613930.0,
      "text": "which broke out in 2009 in Argentina and worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 614490.0,
      "end_time": 617520.0,
      "text": "When the first cases began to come to light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 617520.0,
      "end_time": 621360.0,
      "text": "we, here in Argentina, were entering the winter season."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 621910.0,
      "end_time": 624120.0,
      "text": "We knew absolutely nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 624120.0,
      "end_time": 625530.0,
      "text": "Everything was a mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 625530.0,
      "end_time": 630900.0,
      "text": "People wore masks on the street, ran into pharmacies to buy alcohol gel."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 630900.0,
      "end_time": 634250.0,
      "text": "People would line up in pharmacies to get a vaccine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 634250.0,
      "end_time": 636810.0,
      "text": "without even knowing if it was the right vaccine"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 636810.0,
      "end_time": 639349.0,
      "text": "that would protect them against this new virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 639350.0,
      "end_time": 641650.0,
      "text": "We knew absolutely nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 641650.0,
      "end_time": 646480.0,
      "text": "At that time, in addition to doing my fellowship at the Infant Foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 646740.0,
      "end_time": 650650.0,
      "text": "I worked as a home pediatrician for a prepaid medicine company."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 651670.0,
      "end_time": 654910.0,
      "text": "I remember that I started my shift at 8 a.m.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 654910.0,
      "end_time": 659600.0,
      "text": "and by 8, I already had a list of 50 scheduled visits."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 659600.0,
      "end_time": 661939.0,
      "text": "It was chaos; people didn&#39;t know what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 662860.0,
      "end_time": 667410.0,
      "text": "I remember the types of patients that I was examining."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 667690.0,
      "end_time": 672500.0,
      "text": "The patients were a little older than what we were used to seeing in winter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 672500.0,
      "end_time": 674390.0,
      "text": "with longer fevers."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 674390.0,
      "end_time": 678690.0,
      "text": "And I mentioned that to my fellowship mentor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 678700.0,
      "end_time": 681590.0,
      "text": "and he, for his part, had heard the same from a colleague,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 681590.0,
      "end_time": 684320.0,
      "text": "about the large number of pregnant women"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 684320.0,
      "end_time": 686100.0,
      "text": "and young adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 686100.0,
      "end_time": 688250.0,
      "text": "being hospitalized in intensive care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 688250.0,
      "end_time": 691160.0,
      "text": "with hard-to-manage clinical profiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 692760.0,
      "end_time": 698600.0,
      "text": "At that time, we set out to understand what was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 699300.0,
      "end_time": 702420.0,
      "text": "First thing Monday morning, we took the car"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 702420.0,
      "end_time": 705349.0,
      "text": "and went to a hospital in Buenos Aires Province,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 705350.0,
      "end_time": 711200.0,
      "text": "that served as a referral hospital for cases of the new influenza virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 711200.0,
      "end_time": 713550.0,
      "text": "We arrived at the hospital; it was crowded."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 713550.0,
      "end_time": 717469.0,
      "text": "All health staff were dressed in NASA-like bio-safety suits."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 717470.0,
      "end_time": 719670.0,
      "text": "We all had face masks in our pockets."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 719670.0,
      "end_time": 722400.0,
      "text": "I, being a hypochondriac, didn&#39;t breathe for two hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 722400.0,
      "end_time": 725520.0,
      "text": "But we could see what was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 725520.0,
      "end_time": 729210.0,
      "text": "Immediately, we started reaching out to pediatricians"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 729210.0,
      "end_time": 733430.0,
      "text": "from six hospitals in the city and in Buenos Aires Province."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 733440.0,
      "end_time": 736770.0,
      "text": "Our main goal was to find out"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 736770.0,
      "end_time": 740660.0,
      "text": "how this new virus behaved in contact with our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 740660.0,
      "end_time": 743240.0,
      "text": "in the shortest time possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 743240.0,
      "end_time": 746200.0,
      "text": "A marathon work."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 746200.0,
      "end_time": 749700.0,
      "text": "In less than three months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 749700.0,
      "end_time": 755160.0,
      "text": "we could see what effect this new H1N1 virus had"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 755160.0,
      "end_time": 761300.0,
      "text": "on the 251 children hospitalized by this virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 761520.0,
      "end_time": 765500.0,
      "text": "We could see which children got more seriously ill:"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 765500.0,
      "end_time": 769120.0,
      "text": "children under four, especially those less than one year old;"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 769120.0,
      "end_time": 771920.0,
      "text": "patients with neurological diseases;"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 771920.0,
      "end_time": 775209.0,
      "text": "and young children with chronic pulmonary diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 775210.0,
      "end_time": 780200.0,
      "text": "Identifying these at-risk groups was important"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 780200.0,
      "end_time": 782730.0,
      "text": "to include them as priority groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 782730.0,
      "end_time": 785730.0,
      "text": "in the recommendations for getting the influenza vaccine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 785730.0,
      "end_time": 787590.0,
      "text": "not only here in Argentina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 787590.0,
      "end_time": 791650.0,
      "text": "but also in other countries which the pandemic not yet reached."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 792750.0,
      "end_time": 794430.0,
      "text": "A year later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 794430.0,
      "end_time": 799520.0,
      "text": "when a vaccine against the pandemic H1N1 virus became available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 799520.0,
      "end_time": 802240.0,
      "text": "we wanted to see what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 802240.0,
      "end_time": 805410.0,
      "text": "After a huge vaccination campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 805410.0,
      "end_time": 810180.0,
      "text": "aimed at protecting at-risk groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 810180.0,
      "end_time": 817140.0,
      "text": "these hospitals, with 93 percent of the at-risk groups vaccinated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 817140.0,
      "end_time": 820770.0,
      "text": "had not hospitalized a single patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 820770.0,
      "end_time": 823449.0,
      "text": "for the pandemic H1N1 virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 823450.0,
      "end_time": 826500.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 827920.0,
      "end_time": 831880.0,
      "text": "In 2009: 251."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 833490.0,
      "end_time": 836440.0,
      "text": "In 2010: zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 836440.0,
      "end_time": 841220.0,
      "text": "Vaccination is an act of individual responsibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 841220.0,
      "end_time": 845250.0,
      "text": "but it has a huge collective impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 846790.0,
      "end_time": 851410.0,
      "text": "If I get vaccinated, not only am I protecting myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 851420.0,
      "end_time": 854630.0,
      "text": "but I am also protecting others."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 855520.0,
      "end_time": 857890.0,
      "text": "Sol had whooping cough."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 859500.0,
      "end_time": 861700.0,
      "text": "Sol was very young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 861700.0,
      "end_time": 866230.0,
      "text": "and she hadn&#39;t yet received her first vaccine against whooping cough."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 867160.0,
      "end_time": 870959.0,
      "text": "I still wonder what would have happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 870960.0,
      "end_time": 876870.0,
      "text": "if everyone around Sol had been vaccinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 877740.0,
      "end_time": 879800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}